<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>상품 수정 | DAMORE ADMIN</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #fff;
      --black: #111;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17,17,17,0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --max: 920px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard","Noto Sans KR",Arial,sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--black);
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    input, textarea, select, button { font: inherit; }

    .container {
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--black);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    .head {
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .head small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .head h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .form-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .row-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    input[type="number"],
    textarea,
    select,
    input[type="file"] {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      outline: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 140px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .note {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .thumb {
      width: 180px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f0ede8;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .thumb img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .thumb-empty {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .stock-box {
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .stock-box strong {
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .check-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .check-row input {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
    }

    .btn-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .btn {
      min-width: 180px;
      height: 52px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container { padding: 0 16px; }
      .row-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .btn { width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">DAMORE ADMIN PANEL</div>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="head">
        <small>Product Edit</small>
        <h1>상품 수정</h1>
        <p>상품 수정에서 재고 수량을 직접 바꿀 수 있는 버전입니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <form method="POST" action="/admin/products/<%= product._id %>/edit" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-grid">
          <div>
            <label>상품명</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= product.name %>" required />
          </div>

          <div class="row-2">
            <div>
              <label>카테고리</label>
              <select name="category" required>
                <% categories.forEach(category => { %>
                  <option value="<%= category.name %>" <%= product.category === category.name ? 'selected' : '' %>>
                    <%= category.name %>
                  </option>
                <% }) %>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label>태그</label>
              <input type="text" name="tag" value="<%= product.tag || '' %>" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row-2">
            <div>
              <label>판매가</label>
              <input type="number" name="price" min="0" value="<%= product.price %>" required />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label>기존가</label>
              <input type="number" name="oldPrice" min="0" value="<%= product.oldPrice || 0 %>" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row-2">
            <div>
              <label>재고 수량</label>
              <input type="number" name="stock" min="0" value="<%= product.stock || 0 %>" required />
              <div class="note">여기서 재고 개수를 직접 수정하면 된다.</div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label>현재 재고 상태</label>
              <div class="stock-box">
                현재 재고:
                <strong><%= product.stock || 0 %>개</strong><br />
                현재 상태:
                <strong><%= (product.stock || 0) > 0 ? '판매중' : '품절' %></strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label>옵션</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="options"
              value="<%= product.options && product.options.length ? product.options.join(', ') : '' %>"
              placeholder="예: S, M, L"
            />
            <div class="note">쉼표로 구분해서 입력 가능</div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label>상품 설명</label>
            <textarea name="desc"><%= product.desc || '' %></textarea>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label>현재 이미지</label>
            <div class="thumb">
              <% if (product.image) { %>
                <img src="<%= product.image %>" alt="<%= product.name %>" />
              <% } else { %>
                <div class="thumb-empty">이미지 없음</div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label>새 이미지 업로드</label>
            <input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" />
          </div>

          <div class="check-row">
            <input type="checkbox" name="isBest" id="isBest" <%= product.isBest ? 'checked' : '' %> />
            <label for="isBest" style="margin:0;">베스트 상품으로 지정</label>
          </div>

          <div class="btn-row">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">상품 수정 저장</button>
            <a href="/admin/products" class="btn btn-light">상품목록으로</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>